{"title":"公共设施","shareable":true,"contact":true,"content":[{"tag":"title","text":"洗漱区"},{"tag":"text","type":"p","text":["洗漱区全天供应冷水。生活热水每日使用量固定为 18 升(部分新生新生需要先在生活用水补助机上刷卡进行激活，激活时间为24 - 48小时)，超过 18 升按照 ￥0.2/升 扣除，可以自行到生活用水补助机处充值。寝室楼下就设有生活用水补助机。"],"style":"text-indent: 1.5em; "},{"tag":"text","heading":"热水供应时间","text":["本部校区:","5:00-8:00，21:00-23:00","净月校区:","6:00-8:00，19:00-22:00(天华公寓全天供应)"]},{"tag":"list","content":[{"text":"如何激活生活用水","icon":"/icon/tabPage/card.svg","path":"card/prepare"}]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm6.jpg","desc":"图为本部三舍AB洗漱区"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm7.jpg","desc":"图为本部三舍C洗漱区"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm8.jpg","desc":"图为净月公寓洗漱区"},{"tag":"title","text":"卫生间"},{"tag":"text","type":"p","text":["卫生间处在公共区域，有阿姨定期打扫卫生，很整洁。"],"style":"text-indent: 1.5em; "},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/toilet.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/toilet2.jpg"},{"tag":"title","text":"其他设施"},{"tag":"text","type":"p","heading":"吹风机","text":["女生寝室楼每层楼都有一个或两个吹风机，插一卡通就可以使用。"],"style":"text-indent: 1.5em; "},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm9.jpg"},{"tag":"text","type":"p","heading":"洗衣机","text":["洗衣机是单筒洗衣机，可洗可甩干。大部分寝室楼的每个楼层有两个洗衣机(三舍 B 一台)。洗衣机为刷卡使用。根据所需洗涤方式刷卡，刷卡完毕后将洗衣机盖关闭即可洗衣, 洗衣用的洗衣液或洗衣粉需自己准备，在洗衣前加入洗衣机内。"],"style":"text-indent: 1.5em; "},{"tag":"list","content":[{"text":"洗衣机详细使用说明","icon":"/module/icon/washer.svg","path":"dorm/washer"}]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm10.jpg"},{"tag":"text","type":"p","heading":"直饮水机","text":["刷卡分别可以接冷/常温/热的饮用水，学校每天免费供应90秒使用时长(约 2 - 4 升，视直饮机水压)，全天供应。超出部分收取制水成本费用，热水 0.3元/升，常温水 0.2元/升。直饮水服务所需的额外费用，是使用校园卡小钱包内的余额，师生可以在自助终端机上进行一卡通小钱包充值。"],"style":"text-indent: 1.5em; "},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm11.jpg"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm12.jpg"},{"tag":"title","text":"自习室"},{"tag":"text","type":"p","text":["寝室楼内每层均设有自习室。自习室不间断供电。"],"style":"text-indent: 1.5em; "},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm13.jpg","desc":"三舍A自习室"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm14.jpg","desc":"三舍B自习室"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm15.jpg","desc":"三舍C自习室"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm16.jpg","desc":"天华公寓自习室"},{"tag":"title","text":"电梯"},{"tag":"text","type":"p","text":["三舍作为高层建筑，A 座、C 座拥有四台电梯，B 拥有三台电梯，客梯不停低楼层，入住时可以使用货梯。请注意客梯是分为单层客梯和双层客梯的，楼下一楼电梯入口处有明确的指示牌。净月寝室没有电梯。(搬行李的时候送你一句: 加油！奥里给！)"],"style":"text-indent: 1.5em; "},{"tag":"img","src":"https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm17.jpg","desc":"三舍电梯"},{"tag":"footer","author":"Mr.Hope","time":"2020年7月18日"}],"images":["https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm6.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm7.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm8.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/toilet.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/toilet2.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm9.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm10.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm11.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm12.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm13.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm14.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm15.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm16.jpg","https://v3.mp.innenu.comcom/img/dorm/dorm17.jpg"],"id":"dorm/public"}